          <h1 class="jumbotron-heading text-muted">A Little Introduction</h1>
          <p class="lead text-muted">Several years ago I moved 1200 miles from my home of over 15 years to move back to Texas for family matters. I was laid off during that time and started a new career.</p>
          <p>It was fun for awhile but 7 years or so later I started to miss coding and as fortune favors me, I was an accident and have been unable to work for the last several months. I started looking back at my prevous life and decided I needed to do something about it. I've learned a new language, some of the basics of the popular frameworks used today, and all the great things javascript has been doing since I left. I decided to get back to writing code again. Some of the names have changed but the game is the same.</p>
          <p>That being said, some of these examples are old and outdated but the fact that these applications, I helped design and run, are still going with the same old code some 6-10 years later hakes me happy.</p>
        </div>
