			      <p class="card-text">A new portal site project for an existing shop. The owner primarily sells items throught their existign Etsy shop but wanted to have their own domain to shocase product sales, provide a single location to act as an information portal site as well as manage an email list and post relevant buisiness related articles</p>
			      <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
			        <div class="btn-group">
			          <a href="https://www.github.com/oxygen545/fmn-apothecary"><button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">GitHub</button></a>&nbsp;
